Author: Ricky Algo
Body: Detect access all password at wifi network

Author: Martin Hall
Subject: Excellent little app
Body: Very useful, I like the way the whole app can be locked with a pin or a fingerprint (on a device that has a fingerprint scanner of course).

Author: Ibrahim Toure
Body: Useful for sharing wifi passwords on the go !

Author: Tawfeeq Van der Veldt
Body: Super goed maar als je even het verkeerde wachtwoord invoert is de qr code ook verkeerd

Author: Mich Capich
Subject: Very handy and easy to use, but not complete...
Body: Great and handy app. Works as it should, with PIN-lock. Just superb! But I miss 2 options... Order the list, with known passwords first/at top, and a backup-feature (encrypted with the same PIN-lock?). Implant these, and 5 stars will be yours! 😃
